title: Send all remaining tokens from Aragon entity to Gnosis Safe
body:
As can be seen [here](https://etherscan.io/address/0xb8541e73aa47a847fa39e803d19a3f9b1bbc5a6c), the mStableDAO's Aragon entity still has a material amount of tokens in its custody. 

Given the Gnosis Safe is the entity that now custodies the majority of the DAO's public treasury, it is motioned to move all remaining tokens from the Aragon entity to the Gnosis Safe. This includes any proceeds from the redemption of BPT tokens currently held, alongside 13,210 BAL tokens.

**Should all remaining tokens from the Aragon entity be sent to the Gnosis Safe at 0x3dd46846eed8D147841AE162C8425c08BD8E1b41?**
author: 0x908DB31Ce01DC42c8B712f9156E969bc65023119
